          "label": "Golden Preview",
          "value": "已加载 translation-reference.json",
          "citation": "translation-reference.json",
          "richTextHtml": "<section class=\"fixture-section\">\n  <header class=\"fixture-section-header\">\n    <h3>Quality / 面料与核心卖点</h3>\n    <p>提炼面料性能要求和核心卖点，适合业务与样衣团队对齐理解。</p>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"fixture-segment-list\">\n    <div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">VALUE DRIVER: &quot;Drop-in&quot; side pockets</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">核心卖点：侧插袋设计</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Wrinkle free fabric</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">抗皱面料</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Glued bottom hem</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">贴合下摆工艺</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Quality spec: Lightweight fabric, quick dry and moisture wicking. 4-way stretch and wrinkle free. Should be able to have glued edges. Plain jersey / no structure with a good &quot;body&quot; not flimsy, but more spongy. More or less the fabric below, please advice if you believe it is a good fit.</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">面料要求：轻薄面料，具备快干排湿功能；四面弹力且抗皱；需支持无缝胶合工艺；采用平纹针织结构，面料需有骨感、不软塌，并带有偏海绵感的柔软手感。请根据下方参考面料评估是否合适。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"fixture-section\">\n  <header class=\"fixture-section-header\">\n    <h3>Construction / 款式结构</h3>\n    <p>概览整件半裙的主要结构要求。</p>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"fixture-segment-list\">\n    <div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Lightweight skirt with double pockets at side</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">轻薄半裙，侧边双口袋设计</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Pocket at CB in waist seam</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">后中腰缝位置增加口袋</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Filled piping detail at front and back</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">前后片增加夹牙滚边细节</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Glued hem at bottom</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">下摆采用贴合工艺</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Folded waist with elastic at waist</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">折叠式松紧腰头</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Inner shorts attached to skirt</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">裙身内置短裤衬里</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Rubber logo front and back</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">前后位置均有硅胶 Logo</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"fixture-section\">\n  <header class=\"fixture-section-header\">\n    <h3>Details OP1 / 细节方案一</h3>\n    <p>细节定位、口袋结构和下摆标注。</p>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"fixture-segment-list\">\n    <div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Rubber logo glued to fabric, 53x13 mm wide, upraised print. Centered, 2 cm from waist. Artwork sent separately.</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">硅胶 Logo，尺寸 53x13mm，立体压印效果；居中放置，距腰线 2cm；图稿另发。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Open pocket at CB, 12 cm wide, see sep image for reference</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">后中开口袋，宽 12cm，具体结构参照单独图片。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Filled piping in contrast colour</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">撞色夹牙滚边。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Double layer shell pocket, folded and glued top</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">双层面料口袋，口袋顶端折叠并做贴合处理。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">New inner shorts, see next page for details</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">新增内置短裤，详见下一页。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Rubber logo glued to fabric, 18x15 mm wide, upraised print. 3 cm from hem, 1.5 cm from piping.</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">另一处硅胶 Logo，尺寸 18x15mm，距下摆 3cm，距夹牙滚边 1.5cm。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Glued hem, slight shaped front and back</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">贴合下摆，前后幅做轻微造型。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"fixture-section\">\n  <header class=\"fixture-section-header\">\n    <h3>Inner Shorts / 内置短裤</h3>\n    <p>重点关注短裤的隐形效果、防滑功能和口袋设计。</p>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"fixture-segment-list\">\n    <div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Logo rubber print inside leg as grip function to prevent shorts from moving upwards</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">裤腿内侧增加硅胶 Logo 防滑带，用于防止短裤上移。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Slanting side pocket, glued hem for flat appearance</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">侧边斜插袋，口袋边缘采用贴合工艺，保证外观平整。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">New inner shorts for least visible appearance</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">新版内置短裤，目标是尽量降低外观显露感。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">No CF seam</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">去除前中缝。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Glued hems or similar flat and clean making</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">裤腿边缘采用无缝贴合或类似的平整工艺。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Slanting pocket at right-hand side</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">右侧设斜插袋。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"fixture-section\">\n  <header class=\"fixture-section-header\">\n    <h3>Details OP2 / 细节方案二</h3>\n    <p>方案二在方案一基础上增加开衩与不同滚边处理。</p>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"fixture-segment-list\">\n    <div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Please send 2 samples, one with slit (opt 2) and one with piping (opt 1)</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">请提供两件样品：一件做开衩（方案二），一件做夹牙滚边（方案一）。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Rubber logo glued to fabric, 53x13 mm wide, upraised print. Centered, 2 cm from waist.</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">后腰下方居中位置放置 53x13mm 硅胶 Logo，距腰顶 2cm。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Seam stitched and turned</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">缝线结构改为车缝后翻处理。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Double layer shell pocket, folded and glued top</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">双层面料口袋，口袋顶端做贴合工艺。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Slit at seam, 8 cm high</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">侧缝位置开衩，高度 8cm。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Glued hem, slight shaped front and back</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">下摆贴合处理，前后幅略微塑形。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"fixture-section\">\n  <header class=\"fixture-section-header\">\n    <h3>References &amp; Colours / 参考图与配色</h3>\n    <p>用于打样时快速回查结构参考和颜色定义。</p>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"fixture-segment-list\">\n    <div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Reference: open pocket CB</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">参考图：后中腰顶口袋。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Reference: Rubber logo print inside leg</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">参考图：裤腿内侧 Logo 防滑带。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Body: Navy</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">大身面料：藏青色。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Inner shorts: DTM</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">内置短裤：顺大身面料色。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Thread: DTM</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">缝纫线：顺大身面料色。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Piping: White</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">滚边：白色。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Bird: White</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">飞鸟图案：白色。</p>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"bilingual-block\">\n      <p class=\"source-line\">Macade logo: White</p>\n      <p class=\"translation-line\">Macade 品牌标识：白色。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
